dct_title_s: Exactissima Asiae delineatio, in praecipuas regiones, caeterasq[ue] partes divisa, et denuò in lucem edita
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Scale determined by using graticule method, measured at 30⁰ north. "Extracta ex authenticis tabulis D. Nicolai Witsen ..."
